,{"section":5,"text":"But the keratotic areas with a lace pattern and erosive areas are more concerning.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03523,0.064047,0.080224,0.09022,0.097555,0.0996,0.10263,0.099503,0.095491,0.085861,0.079449,0.070193],"unified_progress":[0.04086,0.073191,0.087488,0.096007,0.1017,0.1019,0.099186,0.09624,0.094981,0.083148,0.06951,0.055791]},{"section":6,"text":"Keratosis usually refers to a buildup of keratin, which can be a sign of various conditions, including some that affect the mucous membranes.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038228,0.061952,0.078276,0.090314,0.096743,0.09969,0.10466,0.1035,0.098355,0.088678,0.076442,0.063163],"unified_progress":[0.036165,0.064028,0.084423,0.096199,0.10185,0.1084,0.10422,0.099694,0.096462,0.086467,0.070187,0.05191]},{"section":7,"text":"I'm considering different possibilities.","dimension":6,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025554,0.05491,0.077782,0.084863,0.096502,0.099638,0.091792,0.093682,0.087668,0.11794,0.088913,0.080756],"unified_progress":[0.03302,0.072121,0.085657,0.10306,0.10029,0.095083,0.09977,0.093864,0.08933,0.095444,0.075201,0.057166]},{"section":8,"text":"Oral leukoplakia comes to mind because it's a common condition where the mucosa thickens and can have a keratotic appearance.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03185,0.059398,0.076532,0.089954,0.098086,0.10109,0.10665,0.10341,0.098306,0.089581,0.078692,0.066455],"unified_progress":[0.033581,0.065001,0.085161,0.10817,0.10503,0.10754,0.10184,0.096727,0.093009,0.080599,0.065811,0.057531]},{"section":9,"text":"It's often associated with smoking or other irritants.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036634,0.059559,0.073454,0.083991,0.09263,0.097821,0.1044,0.10633,0.10334,0.094865,0.082178,0.064796],"unified_progress":[0.04124,0.064903,0.081319,0.092447,0.098048,0.10854,0.10328,0.1011,0.09506,0